text:
This is a bug in org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.optional.starteam.StarTeamCheckout.

At line 411 "stFolder.getName()" should be changed to "stFolder.getPathFragment()".

410  java.io.File subfolder =
411    new java.io.File(targetFolder, stFolder.getPathFragment());
412 // new java.io.File(targetFolder, stFolder.getName());

I'm new to this, so I don't know how to go about getting this fix applied to the base.  I've updated a version on my desktop, but I'd like to get it in the base.
